answers.body_markdown:
You miss to add the dependency for `org.bukkit`.

Add 


    &lt;!-- https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/org.bukkit/bukkit --&gt;
    &lt;dependency&gt;
        &lt;groupId&gt;org.bukkit&lt;/groupId&gt;
